label: aadharNo
comment: The aadhar number issued by the government for the individual corresponding to this observation.

label: panNo
comment: The pan card number of the individual corresponding to this observation.

label: drivingLicense
comment: The driving license number of the individual corresponding to this observation.

label: gstin
comment: The Goods and Service Tax Identification Number of an individual or a business corresponding to this observation.

label: fssaiLicense
comment: The FSSAI (Food and Safety Standards Authority of India) license number.

label: bankAccountNo
comment: The bank account number of the individual or business corresponding to this observation

label: ifscCode
comment: The IFSC code for the bank corresponding to this observation

label: digitalSignature
comment: The link to the digital signature of the entity corresponding to this observation.

label: iec
comment: The Importer-Exporter Code (IEC) which is an unique business identification number for export from or import to India

label: registrationNumber
comment: The registration number of the entity corresponding to this observation.
